NEWTON RAPHSON :
IT IS A NUMERICAL TECHNIQUE TO APPROXIMATE THE ROOTS OF A REAL VALUED FUNCTION . IT USE TANGENT LINES TO THE FUNCTION CURVE TO APPROXIMATE THE ROOT.



ALGORITHM : 











IMPLEMENTATION OF NEWTON RAPHSON METHOD BY C CODE 























